#. <section class="sutta" id="an10.76"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.76:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.76:0.2"
msgid "8. Ākaṅkhavagga"
msgstr "8. If You Want"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.76:0.3"
msgid "76. Tayodhammasutta"
msgstr "76. Three Things"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an10.76:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Tayome, bhikkhave, dhammā loke na saṃvijjeyyuṃ, na tathāgato loke "
"uppajjeyya arahaṃ sammāsambuddho, na tathāgatappavedito dhammavinayo loke "
"dibbeyya."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, if three things were not found, the Realized One, the perfected "
"one, the fully awakened Buddha would not arise in the world, and the "
"teaching and training proclaimed by the Realized One would not shine in the "
"world."

msgctxt "an10.76:1.2"
msgid "Katame tayo?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an10.76:1.3"
msgid "Jāti ca, jarā ca, maraṇañca—"
msgstr "Rebirth, old age, and death."

msgctxt "an10.76:1.4"
msgid ""
"ime kho, bhikkhave, tayo dhammā loke na saṃvijjeyyuṃ, na tathāgato loke "
"uppajjeyya arahaṃ sammāsambuddho, na tathāgatappavedito dhammavinayo loke "
"dibbeyya."
msgstr ""
"If these three things were not found, the Realized One, the perfected one, "
"the fully awakened Buddha would not arise in the world, and the teaching and "
"training proclaimed by the Realized One would not shine in the world."

msgctxt "an10.76:1.5"
msgid ""
"Yasmā ca kho, bhikkhave, ime tayo dhammā loke saṃvijjanti tasmā tathāgato "
"loke uppajjati arahaṃ sammāsambuddho, tasmā tathāgatappavedito dhammavinayo "
"loke dibbati."
msgstr ""
"But since these three things are found, the Realized One, the perfected one, "
"the fully awakened Buddha arises in the world, and the teaching and training "
"proclaimed by the Realized One shines in the world."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an10.76:2.1"
msgid ""
