"maraṇaṃ pahātuṃ."
msgstr ""
"Without giving up three things you can’t give up rebirth, old age, and death."

msgctxt "an10.76:2.2"
msgid "Katame tayo?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an10.76:2.3"
msgid "Rāgaṃ appahāya, dosaṃ appahāya, mohaṃ appahāya—"
msgstr "Greed, hate, and delusion."

# Note that MS counts this as item one, in BB it is item two.
